他每次都把屋子裏弄得烏煙瘴氣
It used to smell up the joint something awful...

1227
01:21:06,220 --> 01:21:09,190
警衛都被熏死了  但他的牛排還真是不錯
and the hacks used to die, but he still cooked a great steak.

1228
01:21:09,360 --> 01:21:11,880
- 你的牛排要怎麼樣  - 半生的
- How do you like yours? - Medium rare.

1229
01:21:12,490 --> 01:21:14,620
半生  貴族一個
Medium rare. An aristocrat.

1230
01:21:15,030 --> 01:21:18,790
當你想到監獄  腦中就會出現像電影中那樣
You know, when you think of prison you get pictures in your mind...

1231
01:21:18,970 --> 01:21:22,600
一排排的人被關在鐵欄杆後面
of all those old movies with rows of guys behind bars.

1232
01:21:22,770 --> 01:21:24,670
對兄弟來說不是那樣的
It wasn't like that for wiseguys.

1233
01:21:24,840 --> 01:21:27,500
並不是那麼槽  除了我很想念吉米
It really wasn't that bad, excepting that I missed Jimmy...

1234
01:21:27,670 --> 01:21:29,070
他在亞特蘭大受刑
who was doing his time in Atlanta.

1235
01:21:29,240 --> 01:21:31,680
順便給我兩塊牛排  好不好
Give me two steaks while you're in there, all right?

1236
01:21:33,150 --> 01:21:37,550
在裏面的人都是嚴格地在受刑  混在一起像豬一樣
Everyone else in the joint was doing real time, mixed together, living like pigs.

1237
01:21:37,720 --> 01:21:40,710
可是我們單獨生活  一切都由我們控制
But we lived alone. We owned the joint.

1238
01:21:40,890 --> 01:21:44,290
用球棒把那兩個狗娘養的臉打爛了  認都認不出來
We batted them sons of bitches. You couldn't recognize them.

1239
01:21:44,460 --> 01:21:45,790
太好了  活該
Good, they deserved it.

1240
01:21:45,960 --> 01:21:49,450
雖然有些警衛不受賄  但他們也不會告發我們
Even the hacks we couldn't bribe would never rat on the guys we did.

1241
01:21:49,630 --> 01:21:51,390
這樣才對  朋友鄰居間應該互相尊重
...had respect. People loved one another.

1242
01:21:51,570 --> 01:21:52,590
夜不閉戶
They left their doors open.

1243
01:21:52,770 --> 01:21:53,760
抱歉  久等了
Sorry it took so long.

1244
01:21:53,930 --> 01:21:56,430
那個瘦子警衛越來越令人討厭了
The skinny guard's getting to be a real pain in the ass.

1245
01:21:56,570 --> 01:21:59,800
- 是該給那個雜種一點教訓了  - 我已經擺平了
- We're gonna have to do something. - I took care of him.

1246
01:21:59,970 --> 01:22:01,670
你帶了些什麼來
What'd you bring?

1247
01:22:01,840 --> 01:22:03,330
- 麵包  - 好
- Bread. - Good.

1248
01:22:03,640 --> 01:22:05,910
- 才烤出來的  - 韋力  你的辣椒和洋蔥有了
- Fresh. - Vinnie, I got your peppers and onions.

1249
01:22:06,080 --> 01:22:08,380
香腸  火腿  還有很多奶酪
Salami, prosciutto, a lot of cheese.

1250
01:22:08,550 --> 01:22:10,040
還有呢  還有什麼別的
Come on, what else?

1251
01:22:10,220 --> 01:22:11,710
- 威士忌  - 好
- Scotch. - Nice.

1252
01:22:12,720 --> 01:22:14,550
- 紅酒  - 好了
- Some red wine. - Okay.

1253
01:22:14,890 --> 01:22:16,750
- 我們可以吃了  - 我也拿了白葡萄酒
- Now we can eat. - I got some white, too.

1254
01:22:16,920 --> 01:22:18,690
白葡萄酒也給我  太美了
Give me the white, too. Beautiful.

1255
01:22:18,860 --> 01:22:21,850
來吧  夥計們  我們可以吃了  已經好了  韋力
Okay, boys, let's eat. Come on, it's ready, Vinnie.

1256
01:22:22,430 --> 01:22:23,520
這裏還有些麵包
Some more bread.

1257
01:22:23,700 --> 01:22:26,360
明天我們吃三明治  你該節食了  韋力
Tomorrow we eat sandwiches. You got to go on a diet, Vinnie.

1258
01:22:26,530 --> 01:22:28,590
- 你別開玩笑了  - 你最好聽我的
- You must be kidding. - Believe me.

1259
01:22:37,880 --> 01:22:39,510
你在忙什麼
What are you doing?

1260
01:22:44,620 --> 01:22:46,480
我也來一點
I'll take that.

1261
01:22:48,890 --> 01:22:51,380
- 好  晚一點見  - 對
- All right, I'll catch you guys later. - Yeah.

1262
01:22:51,530 --> 01:22:53,820
去公園散散步  是不是
You going for a walk in the park?

1263
01:22:55,360 --> 01:22:58,490
- 好  下禮拜見  謝謝  - 好
- Okay, I'll catch you next week. Thanks. - Okay.

1264
01:23:01,300 --> 01:23:03,900
- 還有沒有  - 沒了  全光了  週末愉快
- Is there any more? - No, that's it. Have a good weekend.

1265
01:23:04,070 --> 01:23:05,060
- 謝啦  - 亨利  再見了
- Thanks. - You too, Henry.

1266
01:23:17,880 --> 01:23:19,080
來
Come on.

1267
01:23:19,620 --> 01:23:21,680
好好站在這兒
You girls stay right here.

1268
01:23:22,090 --> 01:23:25,350
- 你們兩個牽著手  - 好了  一直走到前面去
- I want you to hold hands. - Okay, go right up to the front.

1269
01:23:25,660 --> 01:23:27,590
- 走吧  - 你好嗎
- Let's go. - How you doing?

1270
01:23:27,760 --> 01:23:30,200
- 還行  你呢  - 很好  謝謝你
- Good, how are you? - Very well, thank you.

1271
01:23:42,240 --> 01:23:44,800
- 你講什麼呀  - 我在登記簿上看到她的名字了
- What you talking about? - I saw her name in the register.

1272
01:23:44,980 --> 01:23:47,040
- 老天呀  - 你要她來看你嗎
- Jesus Christ. - You want her to visit you?

1273
01:23:47,210 --> 01:23:51,010
讓她為你哭整晚不睡  還寫信給假釋管理局
Let her stay up all night crying and writing letters to the parole board.

1274
01:23:51,180 --> 01:23:54,150
你以為我在這兒做什麼  我在坐牢呀
What am I doing here? Where am I? I'm in jail.

1275
01:23:54,390 --> 01:23:56,580
我不能阻止別人來看我呀
I can't stop people from coming to see me.

1276
01:23:56,760 --> 01:24:00,020
好呀  讓她每星期替你偷運這些東西進來
Good, let her sneak this stuff in for you every week.

1277
01:24:00,190 --> 01:24:04,820
- 讓她每星期來和那些雜種警衛打交道  - 你這是幹什麼
- Let her fight these bastards every week! - Look what you're doing! Stop it!

1278
01:24:06,300 --> 01:24:07,530
很抱歉
I'm sorry.

1279
01:24:08,030 --> 01:24:10,530
讓她來替你把這些狗屎運進來
Let her sneak this shit in for you.

1280
01:24:11,540 --> 01:24:13,400
你夠了沒有  凱倫
Will you stop it, Karen?

1281
01:24:13,840 --> 01:24:16,400
- 讓她去做所有的事嘛  - 夠了
- Let her do it! - Stop it!

1282
01:24:24,580 --> 01:24:27,950
我好孤獨  沒有人要幫我
Nobody's helping me. I'm all alone.

1283
01:24:28,890 --> 01:24:30,910
貝兒和摩裏都破產了
Belle and Morrie are broke.

1284
01:24:31,320 --> 01:24:34,520
我向你的朋友利摩討他欠你的錢
I asked your friend Remo for the money that he owes you.

1285
01:24:34,690 --> 01:24:36,060
你知道他說什麼嗎
You know what he told me?

1286
01:24:36,230 --> 01:24:39,820
他叫我把孩子們帶到警察局去領救濟金
He told me to take my kids down to the police station and get on welfare.

1287
01:24:40,000 --> 01:24:41,970
一切會過去的
It's gonna be okay.

1288
01:24:42,170 --> 01:24:46,270
就連保利  他出去後我也沒見到他  我都沒見到他們了
Even Paulie, since he got out, I've never seen him. I never see anybody anymore.

1289
01:24:46,440 --> 01:24:49,200
只有我們兩個了
It's only you and me. That's what happens when you go away.

1290
01:24:49,380 --> 01:24:53,370
我告訴過你  一旦進了牢就孤立了  忘掉所有的人  忘掉保利
I told you that we're on our own. Forget everybody else. Forget Paulie.

1291
01:24:54,380 --> 01:24:58,370
他在保釋期間是不會幫任何人做任何事的
As long as he's on parole, he doesn't want anybody doing anything.

1292
01:25:00,850 --> 01:25:03,190
- 我受不了了  - 你能夠忍受  聽我說
- I can't do it. - Yes, you can. Listen to me.

1293
01:25:03,360 --> 01:25:05,850
你只要不斷把東西帶來
All I need is for you is to keep bringing me the stuff.

1294
01:25:06,030 --> 01:25:08,620
這裏有個從匹茲堡來的  他會幫我銷貨
I got a guy in here from Pittsburgh who'll help me move it.

1295
01:25:08,800 --> 01:25:10,520
一個月後我們就安定了
In a month we're gonna be fine.

1296
01:25:10,520 --> 01:25:13,050
- 我們不需要別人  - 我害怕
- We won't need anybody. - I'm afraid.

1297
01:25:13,170 --> 01:25:15,100
我怕萬一保利知道你私下在販毒
I'm afraid if Paulie finds out...

1298
01:25:15,270 --> 01:25:16,720
我不是說了嗎  不要擔心保利
Don't worry about him.

1299
01:25:16,720 --> 01:25:20,770
他並沒有幫我們呀  他有沒有供應食物給我們
He is not helping us out. Is he putting any food on the table?

1300
01:25:21,440 --> 01:25:22,930
我們只有彼此幫助
We've gotta help each other.

1301
01:25:23,080 --> 01:25:26,740
我們的行動一定要特別特別小心
We've just gotta be really careful while we do it.

1302
01:25:31,420 --> 01:25:33,910
別讓我再聽到她的名字
I don't want to hear a word about her anymore.

1303
01:25:34,090 --> 01:25:35,110
永遠不會了
Never.

1304
01:25:37,890 --> 01:25:40,720
四年後

1305
01:26:00,210 --> 01:26:01,870
爸爸
Daddy!

1306
01:26:03,480 --> 01:26:05,750
- 我們好想念你  - 你會待下來嗎
- We missed you. - Are you here to stay?

1307
01:26:05,920 --> 01:26:09,450
你看到我們的畫沒有  那張房子和彩虹是我畫的
Did you see our pictures? I did the one with the house and rainbow.

1308
01:26:09,620 --> 01:26:11,110
太陽是我畫的
I did the sun.

1309
01:26:11,260 --> 01:26:15,160
我的合唱團兩星期後有音樂會  你能來嗎
My chorus concert is in two weeks. Are you coming?

1310
01:26:16,000 --> 01:26:17,860
喜歡我們的房子嗎
Do you like the house?

1311
01:26:19,130 --> 01:26:21,160
凱倫  收拾行李  我們要搬家了
Karen, get packed. We're moving out of here.

1312
01:26:21,330 --> 01:26:22,390
怎麼搬
With what?

1313
01:26:22,600 --> 01:26:25,700
不用擔心  去找新房子就好了
Don't worry, with what. Just start looking for a new house.

1314
01:26:25,870 --> 01:26:29,270
明早我要去匹茲堡  那邊有幾個人欠我一萬五千元
I got to go to Pittsburgh in the morning. Those guys there owe me $15,000.

1315
01:26:29,440 --> 01:26:31,380
我們沒事了  我都安排好了
We'll be all right. I got things lined up.

1316
01:26:31,540 --> 01:26:34,210
匹茲堡  你明天要去向你的假釋官報到呀
Pittsburgh? You have to go see your parole officer tomorrow.

1317
01:26:34,380 --> 01:26:37,280
凱倫  不要操心了  一切都會沒問題的
Don't worry about it. Everything's gonna be fine.

1318
01:26:37,980 --> 01:26:40,350
- 誰要去保利伯伯家  - 我
- Who wants to go to Uncle Paulie's? - Me!

1319
01:26:50,660 --> 01:26:52,260
你要什麼
What do you want?

1320
01:26:52,500 --> 01:26:54,520
甜心  讓媽媽好好吃飯
Sweetheart, let Mommy eat.

1321
01:26:58,000 --> 01:27:00,870
氣色不錯  牢裏有吃得這麼好嗎
You look good. Did you eat this good in the joint?

1322
01:27:03,010 --> 01:27:04,870
不要再搞那些勾當了
I don't want any more of that shit.

1323
01:27:05,050 --> 01:27:06,030
什麼勾當
What shit?

1324
01:27:06,210 --> 01:27:08,810
- 離那些垃圾遠一點  - 保利
- Just stay away from the garbage. - Look, Paulie...

1325
01:27:08,980 --> 01:27:12,180
你在裏面做了我不管  你是身不由己
I'm not talking about what you did inside. You did what you had to do.

1326
01:27:12,350 --> 01:27:14,910
我指現在  從現在  從這裏開始
I'm talking about now. From now. Here and now.

1327
01:27:15,960 --> 01:27:18,690
- 我怎麼會搞那些  - 不要把我當傻瓜
- Why would I get into that? - Don't make a jerk out of me.

1328
01:27:18,860 --> 01:27:20,420
千萬不要
Just don't do it.

1329
01:27:24,160 --> 01:27:27,130
現在  我要跟你談吉米  你要注意他
I want to talk to you about Jimmy. You gotta watch out for him.

1330
01:27:27,300 --> 01:27:30,030
他很能賺錢  但他太狂了  太冒險了
He's a good earner, but he's wild, takes too many chances.

1331
01:27:30,200 --> 01:27:32,690
我瞭解吉米  你想我會像他那樣冒險嗎
I know Jimmy. You think I would take chances like him?

1332
01:27:32,840 --> 01:27:34,600
湯米也是個好孩子  但他太瘋了
Tommy's a good kid, but he's crazy.

1333
01:27:34,770 --> 01:27:36,500
他是個牛仔  他樣樣都想表現
He's a cowboy. He's got too much to prove.

1334
01:27:36,680 --> 01:27:38,300
你不能不自己小心
You gotta watch out for kids like this.

1335
01:27:38,480 --> 01:27:41,070
我太清楚他們的個性了  我只利用他們做些事
I know what they are. I only use them for certain things.

1336
01:27:41,250 --> 01:27:43,770
我不要像蓋比那樣被人糟蹋  你明白嗎
I ain't gonna get fucked like Gribbs, you understand?

1337
01:27:43,950 --> 01:27:48,280
蓋比已經70歲了  他將老死獄中  那不是我所要的
Gribbs is 70 years old. The fucking guy's gonna die in prison. I don't need that.

1338
01:27:48,620 --> 01:27:52,490
所以我現在警告每一個人  連我兒子在內
So I'm warning everybody. Everybody. Could be my son, could be anybody.

1339
01:27:53,030 --> 01:27:55,550
就因為蓋比手下的人
Gribbs got 20 years just for saying hello to some fuck...

1340
01:27:55,730 --> 01:27:57,820
在他背後販毒  他被判20年
who was sneaking behind his back, selling junk.

1341
01:27:58,000 --> 01:28:00,430
我絕不容許這種事發生在我身上  你懂了嗎
I don't need that. That won't happen to me, understand?

1342
01:28:00,600 --> 01:28:02,730
你能提早出來  是因為我給你找了份工作
You know you're out early because I got you a job.

1343
01:28:02,900 --> 01:28:04,890
我不要整天被條子監視  明白嗎
I don't need this heat, you understand that?

1344
01:28:05,070 --> 01:28:08,970
如果你看到任何人在販毒  你一定要來告訴我
You see anybody fucking around with this shit you're gonna tell me, right?

1345
01:28:09,140 --> 01:28:10,170
不管是誰
That means anybody.

1346
01:28:10,340 --> 01:28:11,330
對不對
All right.

1347
01:28:11,510 --> 01:28:13,070
對  當然
Yeah. Of course.

1348
01:28:20,690 --> 01:28:24,620
我花了一個星期明查暗訪  才把那批匹茲堡貨賣掉
Took me about a week of sneaking around before I could unload the Pittsburgh stuff.

1349
01:28:24,790 --> 01:28:27,280
不過我著實賺了一大筆
But when I did, it was a real score.

1350
01:28:27,430 --> 01:28:29,950
我開始利用珊蒂的家來混合毒品
I started using Sandy's place to mix the stuff.

1351
01:28:30,130 --> 01:28:32,560
雖然她吸的比她配的還多
And even with Sandy snorting more than she mixed...

1352
01:28:32,730 --> 01:28:35,360
但還是利潤極大的生意
I could see that this was a really good business.

1353
01:28:35,540 --> 01:28:37,940
第二個禮拜我就賺了一萬兩千元
I made $12,000 in my second week.

1354
01:28:38,540 --> 01:28:41,600
為我的房子付了頭期款  事情越來越順利了
I had a down payment on my house and things were really rolling.

1355
01:28:41,780 --> 01:28:46,010
我只要偶爾告訴珊蒂我愛她就好了
All I had to do was every once in a while tell Sandy that I loved her.

1356
01:28:49,620 --> 01:28:51,680
這種安排太完美了
But it was perfect, I'm telling you.

1357
01:28:51,850 --> 01:28:54,220
只要貨是從匹茲堡來的
As long as I kept getting the stuff from Pittsburgh...

1358
01:28:54,390 --> 01:28:56,080
保利絕不可能發覺
I knew Paulie would never find out.

1359
01:28:56,260 --> 01:29:00,160
幾個禮拜之後生意做大了  我一個人處理不了
Within a couple of weeks, it got so big I needed some help.

1360
01:29:00,490 --> 01:29:03,290
就把吉米和湯米拉了進來
So I got Jimmy and Tommy to come in with me.

1361
01:29:03,660 --> 01:29:05,220
真夠棒的
It's fucking great.

1362
01:29:05,400 --> 01:29:06,630
康威先生
Mr. Conway.

1363
01:29:12,470 --> 01:29:14,300
- 你薪水單帶來沒有  - 有
- Bring your pay slips? - Yeah.

1364
01:29:14,470 --> 01:29:17,170
保釋部

1365
01:29:17,400 --> 01:29:19,900
興建工程花了四個半月
Four and a half months of dirt.

1366
01:29:20,950 --> 01:29:22,920
- 真好呀  - 撐過來了
- It's so good. - I did it.

1367
01:29:24,080 --> 01:29:26,680
- 你喜歡嗎  - 真是太棒了
- Do you love it? - It's wonderful.

1368
01:29:27,120 --> 01:29:30,890
這個訂做的  你坐坐看  貝兒
And this we just had to have made special. Go ahead, sit in it, Belle.

1369
01:29:31,060 --> 01:29:33,580
有的坐下去真不舒服
The others you couldn't even sit in.

1370
01:29:33,790 --> 01:29:35,280
好了  準備好
Okay, you ready?

1371
01:29:35,460 --> 01:29:37,620
看著石壁
Watch the wall with the rock.

1372
01:29:45,270 --> 01:29:48,070
電工特別設計的
The electricians did it special. Come on.

1373
01:29:49,240 --> 01:29:51,010
來呀  來這邊
Come on. All right.

1374
