01:49:25,180 --> 01:49:27,540
那天早上令吉米高興的原因
What made Jimmy so happy that morning...

1664
01:49:27,710 --> 01:49:30,610
是因為湯米要被引薦
was that this was the day that Tommy was being made.

1665
01:49:30,880 --> 01:49:33,910
他興奮得好像他自己要被引薦似的
Jimmy was so excited, you'd think he was being made.

1666
01:49:34,520 --> 01:49:37,150
他至少打了四次電話到湯米家
He must have made four calls to Tommy's house.

1667
01:49:37,360 --> 01:49:41,290
引薦禮完成之後以信號表示
They had a signal set up, so he'd know the minute the ceremony was over.

1668
01:49:42,160 --> 01:49:44,390
- 媽  你在哪兒  - 在這裏呀
- Ma, where are you? - Here I am.

1669
01:49:45,030 --> 01:49:47,590
- 你回來啦  - 回來  我正要出去呀
- You're home. - Home? I'm leaving.

1670
01:49:48,030 --> 01:49:50,630
- 不錯吧  - 你看起來帥極了
- You look lovely. - I look good, huh?

1671
01:49:50,740 --> 01:49:54,140
千萬小心  恭喜你了  祝你好運
You look wonderful. Be careful. Congratulations.

1672
01:49:54,810 --> 01:49:58,140
我愛你  別再畫宗教畫了  拜託你
I love you. Don't paint any more religious pictures, please.

1673
01:49:58,310 --> 01:49:59,900
- 上帝與你同在  - 再見  媽媽
- God be with you. - Bye, Ma.

1674
01:50:00,080 --> 01:50:02,410
我們都以好兄弟互相稱呼
We always called each other goodfellas.

1675
01:50:02,580 --> 01:50:04,210
你對某人說
You'd say to somebody:

1676
01:50:04,380 --> 01:50:08,580
你會喜歡他  他是好兄弟  是我們一夥的
"You'll like this guy. He's all right. He's a goodfella, one of us."

1677
01:50:08,950 --> 01:50:10,320
你明白嗎
You understand?

1678
01:50:10,990 --> 01:50:13,320
我們都是好兄弟
We were goodfellas. Wiseguys.

1679
01:50:15,790 --> 01:50:19,160
吉米和我都因為有愛爾蘭血統  而不能被引薦
But Jimmy and I could never be made because we had Irish blood.

1680
01:50:19,330 --> 01:50:21,820
即便我母親是西西里人也沒有用
It didn't matter my mother was Sicilian.

1681
01:50:22,030 --> 01:50:25,970
你一定要百分之百意大利血統才能被正式引薦
To become a member of a crew, you've got to be 100% Italian...

1682
01:50:26,140 --> 01:50:29,340
他們要能追蹤出你所有親戚的來歷
so they can trace your relatives back to the old country.

1683
01:50:36,580 --> 01:50:38,810
那是最高的榮譽
It's the highest honor they can give you.

1684
01:50:38,980 --> 01:50:41,480
象徵你已屬於一個家庭  一個團體
It means you belong to a family and a crew.

1685
01:50:41,850 --> 01:50:44,380
那意謂著再沒有人敢傷害你
It means nobody can fuck around with you.

1686
01:50:44,920 --> 01:50:47,320
你卻可以任意欺侮
It also means you could fuck around with anybody...

1687
01:50:47,490 --> 01:50:49,930
那些不屬於任何家族的人
just as long as they aren't also a member.

1688
01:50:50,100 --> 01:50:53,530
好像擁有偷劫的執照  做任何事的執照
It's like a license to steal. A license to do anything.

1689
01:50:55,700 --> 01:50:57,690
你被正式引薦有多少年了
How many years ago since you were made?

1690
01:50:57,870 --> 01:51:00,600
- 我是老人了  30年前  - 30年前呀
- I'm an old-timer. 30 years ago. - Thirty years?

1691
01:51:00,770 --> 01:51:02,510
是呀  有很多值得回憶的事呀
Brings back a lot of memories.

1692
01:51:02,510 --> 01:51:05,040
派克山當時也只不過一粒青春痘嘛
Pike's Peak was a pimple then, wasn't it?

1693
01:51:08,310 --> 01:51:11,280
對吉米來說  湯米被引薦
As far as Jimmy was concerned, with Tommy being made...

1694
01:51:11,450 --> 01:51:13,850
就像我們都被引薦了一樣
it was like we were all being made.

1695
01:51:14,720 --> 01:51:17,250
我們之中有人當了會員了
We would now have one of our own as a member.

1696
01:51:33,240 --> 01:51:34,870
- 是誰  - 是韋力
- Who's this? - This is Vinnie.

1697
01:51:35,040 --> 01:51:37,840
怎麼回事  儀式完成了嗎
Vinnie. What happened? Did we get straightened out?

1698
01:51:38,010 --> 01:51:41,040
發生一點問題  我們盡力了
No, we had a problem. We tried to do everything we could.

1699
01:51:41,210 --> 01:51:42,200
你是什麼意思
What do you mean?

1700
01:51:42,380 --> 01:51:46,510
我是說他死了  我們也無能為力
You know what I mean. He's gone, and we couldn't do nothing about it.

1701
01:51:48,420 --> 01:51:50,290
- 就這樣  - 你是什麼意思
- That's it. - What do you mean?

1702
01:51:50,460 --> 01:51:51,820
他死了
He's gone.

1703
01:51:53,790 --> 01:51:54,820
就這樣
That's it.

1704
01:51:59,730 --> 01:52:02,530
我早就知道會這樣  狗娘養的  我不能相信
I knew it! I can't fucking believe it.

1705
01:52:12,950 --> 01:52:14,070
發生什麼事啦
What happened?

1706
01:52:14,250 --> 01:52:16,410
- 他們幹掉他了  - 操
- They fucking whacked him - Fuck.

1707
01:52:32,230 --> 01:52:33,890
你還好嗎
Are you all right?

1708
01:52:40,970 --> 01:52:43,460
那是替比利·貝茲報仇
It was revenge for Billy Batts...

1709
01:52:43,640 --> 01:52:45,540
還有一些舊的積怨
and a lot of other things.

1710
01:52:45,710 --> 01:52:46,700
就是這樣
And that's that.

1711
01:52:46,880 --> 01:52:49,280
我們是一點辦法也沒有
There was nothing we could do about it.

1712
01:52:49,450 --> 01:52:52,040
貝茲是黑手黨的  湯米還不是
Batts was a made man and Tommy wasn't.

1713
01:52:52,650 --> 01:52:54,590
我們只是老老實實的逆來順受
We had to sit still and take it.

1714
01:52:54,750 --> 01:52:58,190
意大利人圈子就是這樣  一種毫無道理的規定
It was among the Italians. It was real greaseball shit.

1715
01:53:10,840 --> 01:53:12,670
他們甚至打在湯米臉上
They even shot Tommy in the face...

1716
01:53:12,840 --> 01:53:16,300
讓他媽媽不能給他開棺瞻仰
so his mother couldn't give him an open coffin at the funeral.

1717
01:53:21,880 --> 01:53:29,910
1980年5月11日  星期日  上午6點55分

1718
01:54:03,790 --> 01:54:05,620
我本來預備好要忙一整天的
I was gonna be busy all day. I had to drop off some guns at Jimmy's...

1719
01:54:05,790 --> 01:54:09,060
我要拿槍去給吉米配消音器
to match some silencers he had.

1720
01:54:09,160 --> 01:54:12,190
去醫院接我弟弟  帶他回家吃晚飯
I had to pick up my brother at the hospital and drive him home.

1721
01:54:12,360 --> 01:54:14,860
然後去取匹茲堡來的貨
I had to pick up some new Pittsburgh stuff for Lois...

1722
01:54:15,030 --> 01:54:18,200
交給露易絲  讓她將貨空運給亞特蘭大附近的客人
to fly down to some customers I had near Atlanta.

1723
01:54:29,480 --> 01:54:32,940
我馬上就知道他不會要那些槍  我知道我的錢泡湯了
Right away, I knew he didn't want them, and I'd be stuck for the money.

1724
01:54:33,120 --> 01:54:36,820
因為他要我才買的  現在他又不要了
I only bought them because he wanted them, and now he didn't.

1725
01:54:37,560 --> 01:54:41,010
這些有什麼鬼用  一個都配不上  你在搞什麼
What good are these? None of them fit. What's the matter with you?

1726
01:54:41,190 --> 01:54:42,520
我才不付錢呢
I'm not paying for it.

1727
01:54:42,690 --> 01:54:46,360
我一句話也沒講  吉米氣得連再見都沒說
I didn't say a thing. Jimmy was so pissed off, he didn't even say goodbye.

1728
01:54:46,530 --> 01:54:48,970
別再吸毒了  你的腦子都快不管用了
Stop the drugs. They're making your mind into mush!

1729
01:54:49,130 --> 01:54:50,930
- 聽見沒有  - 我把它們帶回去就是了
- You hear me? - I'll take them back.

1730
01:54:55,640 --> 01:54:58,910
上午8點05分

1731
01:55:03,950 --> 01:55:05,920
那些匹茲堡傢伙  總是在買槍
My Pittsburgh guys always wanted guns.

1732
01:55:06,080 --> 01:55:09,680
我下午反正要去見他們  去取貨
Since I would see them in the afternoon to pick up a delivery...

1733
01:55:09,860 --> 01:55:12,380
我蠻肯定我能賺回本的
I was pretty sure I'd get my money back.

1734
01:55:31,410 --> 01:55:32,400
我的老天呀
Oh, my God.

1735
01:55:32,850 --> 01:55:33,650
上午8點45分

1736
01:55:33,650 --> 01:55:38,340
當我終於到了醫院接麥可  醫生說我該住院了
When I finally got to the hospital, Michael's doctor wanted to put me in bed.

1737
01:55:38,480 --> 01:55:40,610
上帝呀  你發生什麼事了
Jesus Christ, what happened to you?

1738
01:55:41,650 --> 01:55:44,020
剛才差點撞車
I almost got into an accident on the way here.

1739
01:55:44,190 --> 01:55:47,090
我描述了車禍  又說昨夜狂歡沒睡
And I told him I was partying all night.

1740
01:55:47,260 --> 01:55:49,060
- 我沒事  - 好啦  到這邊來
- I'm fine. - Come on. Get over here.

1741
01:55:49,230 --> 01:55:51,320
- 醫師  我沒事  - 我給你做個檢查
- Doc, I'm fine. - Let me check you out.

1742
01:55:51,830 --> 01:55:52,990
好啦
Come on.

1743
01:55:56,030 --> 01:55:58,700
他很同情我  只給了我10毫克鎮靜劑
He took mercy on me, gave me 10 milligrams of Valium...

1744
01:55:58,870 --> 01:55:59,930
就讓我回去了
and sent me home.

1745
01:56:00,740 --> 01:56:04,470
我計劃把弟弟送回家  同時把凱倫接上
My plan was to drop off my brother at the house and pick up Karen.

1746
01:56:06,440 --> 01:56:09,680
你看見沒有  一架直升機
There it is. You see that helicopter right there?

1747
01:56:09,850 --> 01:56:13,250
就在我們前面  它跟了我一早上了
Right in front of us, there. I think it's been following me all morning.

1748
01:56:13,520 --> 01:56:16,180
- 別瞎扯了  它跟蹤你幹什麼  - 我告訴你
- Get the fuck out. What are you, nuts? - I'm telling you.

1749
01:56:16,350 --> 01:56:17,550
我也不知道是怎麼回事
I don't know what's going on.

1750
01:56:17,720 --> 01:56:20,750
這是我第三次看到它  我去醫院接你也看到了
It's the third time I've seen it. At the hospital I saw it.

1751
01:56:20,930 --> 01:56:23,450
中途停了兩次  每次都看到它
I had to make some stops. I've seen it every time.

1752
01:56:23,630 --> 01:56:26,030
我跑了好多地方  整天都看到它
I've been all over town and I've seen it all day.

1753
01:56:32,870 --> 01:56:34,600
那天由我做晚餐
I was cooking dinner that night.

1754
01:56:32,870 --> 01:56:34,870
{\an8}上午11點30分

1755
01:56:34,770 --> 01:56:39,270
我必須把肉汁熬出來做蕃茄配料
I had to start braising the beef and veal shanks for the tomato sauce.

1756
01:56:41,950 --> 01:56:45,180
是麥可最喜歡的菜  我做了肉醬
It was Michael's favorite. I was making ziti with meat gravy...

1757
01:56:45,350 --> 01:56:47,840
還打算烤辣椒
and I'm planning to roast some peppers over the flames...

1758
01:56:48,020 --> 01:56:51,960
橄欖油豆  大蒜等
put on some string beans with olive oil. I had some beautiful cutlets...

1759
01:56:52,120 --> 01:56:53,180
我還有切得很好的小牛肉
that were cut just right...

1760
01:56:53,360 --> 01:56:56,350
打算炸好了當開胃菜
that I was going to fry up as an appetizer.

1761
01:56:56,560 --> 01:56:58,500
我在家停留了約一小時
So, I was home for about an hour.

1762
01:56:58,730 --> 01:57:00,700
現在我計劃提早吃晚飯
My plan was to start the dinner early...

1763
01:57:00,870 --> 01:57:03,390
凱倫和我可以把槍推銷掉
so Karen and I could unload the guns Jimmy didn't want...

1764
01:57:03,570 --> 01:57:04,970
同時把貨取回來給露易絲
then get the package for Lois...

1765
01:57:05,140 --> 01:57:07,700
由她跑一趟亞特蘭大
to take to Atlanta for her trip later that night.

1766
01:57:08,570 --> 01:57:12,370
我不時從窗戶看出去  直升機已經不在了
I kept looking out the window, and I saw that the helicopter was gone.

1767
01:57:12,980 --> 01:57:16,470
麥可  注意蕃茄汁好嗎  你留在這裏陪麥可叔叔
Michael, keep an eye on the sauce. Stay here with your Uncle Michael.

1768
01:57:17,620 --> 01:57:21,380
我請麥可注意配料  我和凱倫就出去了
So I asked my brother to watch the sauce, and Karen and I started out.

1769
01:57:24,290 --> 01:57:26,350
天呀  我看見了
Oh, God. I see it.

1770
01:57:26,630 --> 01:57:29,120
- 我看見了  就在那兒  - 該死
- I see it. Look, it's right there. - Damn!

1771
01:57:30,330 --> 01:57:31,760
- 就是它  - 就在那邊
- That's it. - There it is.

1772
01:57:31,930 --> 01:57:33,560
我們去你媽媽家
We got to get to your mother's.

1773
01:57:34,170 --> 01:57:35,430
看見了吧  我告訴你了嘛
See, I told you.

1774
01:57:35,630 --> 01:57:37,000
是很奇怪
It's funny.

1775
01:57:37,400 --> 01:57:40,240
- 但並不是世界末日  - 我們先去你媽媽家
- It's not the end of the world. - We're going to your mother's.

1776
01:58:08,930 --> 01:58:12,700
進去告訴你媽媽  外面的東西不要碰  好嗎
Go inside, tell your mother not to touch anything outside the house. Nothing.

1777
01:58:12,870 --> 01:58:15,530
為什麼不到你媽媽家去  非要到我媽家來
We couldn't go to your mother's house? You had to come here.

1778
01:58:21,110 --> 01:58:22,770
來  去購物吧
Let's go shopping.

1779
01:58:25,020 --> 01:58:27,760
沒有  我沒瘋  這死東西跟了我一早上
I'm not nuts, it's been following me all morning.

1780
01:58:25,900 --> 01:58:27,900
{\an8}中午12點30分

1781
01:58:27,760 --> 01:58:29,280
我跟你講啦
I'm telling you.

1782
01:58:30,420 --> 01:58:33,690
好啦  好啦  他說我疑心病太重
Fine. Fine. He thinks I'm paranoid!

1783
01:58:34,760 --> 01:58:38,160
我應該把直升機帶到他那  看我是不是疑心病
I should bring him the helicopter, then we'll see how paranoid I am.

1784
01:58:40,170 --> 01:58:42,030
我們進去吧
Come on, let's go inside.

1785
01:58:42,570 --> 01:58:45,970
下午1點30分

1786
01:58:46,140 --> 01:58:47,400
不見了
Yeah, it's gone.

1787
01:58:47,570 --> 01:58:50,100
-我聽不見聲音了  -來吧  回你媽媽家
- I don't hear anything. - Let's go back to your mother's.

1788
01:58:56,180 --> 01:58:59,780
下午3點30分

1789
01:59:03,420 --> 01:59:05,980
- 還可以嗎  - 太好了  太好了
- They all right? - Beautiful. They're great.

1790
01:59:06,830 --> 01:59:09,490
我不是說了  你是疑心病嗎  我告訴你  他是多心罷了
Didn't I tell you, you were paranoid? Didn't I tell him?

1791
01:59:09,660 --> 01:59:11,150
是呀  我需要吸一口
Yeah. I need a hit.

1792
01:59:11,730 --> 01:59:14,720
你要看直升機嗎  來  我給你看直升機
Want to see helicopters? Come on, I'll show you helicopters.

1793
01:59:15,370 --> 01:59:17,860
我今天看夠直升機了
I've seen enough helicopters for one day, thank you.

1794
01:59:18,870 --> 01:59:23,200
我計劃先回家  把包裹準備給露易絲帶上路
I had to get home and get the package ready for Lois to take on her trip.

1795
01:59:23,380 --> 01:59:27,240
我還要去珊蒂家  讓她把奎寧注射進去
Also, I had to get to Sandy's to give the package a whack with quinine.

1796
01:59:27,580 --> 01:59:29,810
加上珊蒂一定會囉嗦我沒去陪她
Plus, I knew Sandy would get on my ass.

1797
01:59:29,980 --> 01:59:33,710
我還得做菜  還有幫助露易絲啟程
I had the cooking to finish, and I had to get Lois ready for her trip.

1798
01:59:33,890 --> 01:59:36,410
- 是珊蒂啦  這是怎樣啊  - 她煩得很啦
- It's Sandy. What is this? - She's a pain in the ass.

1799
01:59:38,160 --> 01:59:39,850
- 你什麼時候過來  - 我一小時之內會去
- When are you coming over? - In an hour.

1800
01:59:40,030 --> 01:59:43,020
- 你今天在我這兒過夜吧  - 不行  我要照顧我弟弟
- You staying tonight, right? - I can't. I got my brother tonight.

1801
01:59:43,360 --> 01:59:47,420
好了  別說了  再見
Come on, stop. We'll talk about it later, okay? Goodbye.

1802
01:59:55,070 --> 01:59:57,060
- 哈羅  - 你準備好了沒有
- Hello? - It's me. You ready?

1803
01:59:58,080 --> 02:00:00,910
叫麥可注意不要讓配料太濃  要不停攪拌
Tell Michael not to let the sauce stick. Keep stirring it.

1804
02:00:01,480 --> 02:00:05,310
- 亨利說不要讓配料太濃  - 我在攪拌
- Henry says don't let the sauce stick. - I'm stirring it.

1805
02:00:05,480 --> 02:00:07,310
- 你知道該怎麼做嗎  - 知道  知道
- Listen, you know what to do? - Yeah, yeah.

1806
02:00:07,490 --> 02:00:09,720
不要跟我來  知道  知道  這一套  這是很重要的事
Don't "yeah, yeah" me, Lois. This is important.

1807
02:00:09,890 --> 02:00:12,320
你到外面去再打電話
Make sure you leave the house when you make the call.

1808
02:00:12,490 --> 02:00:15,650
懂不懂  用公用電話  你聽見沒有  不是鬧著玩的
Understand me? Call from an outside line. I mean it.

1809
02:00:15,830 --> 02:00:19,490
上帝  你把我當呆子呀  少煩我  我知道該怎麼做
Jesus, you must think I'm dumb. Why are you bugging me? I know what to do.

