1961
02:10:36,410 --> 02:10:39,010
- 我知道  - 不要忘了  打電話給我
- I'll try. - Don't forget, he's got to call me.

1962
02:10:41,620 --> 02:10:43,810
- 這邊嗎  - 一直走
- Over here? - Right down there.

1963
02:10:58,870 --> 02:11:00,530
一直走  在轉角
It's over there, on the corner.

1964
02:11:01,210 --> 02:11:02,470
就在那裏
Right there.

1965
02:11:36,670 --> 02:11:38,800
不是  去呀  就在裏面
No, go ahead. It's right in there.

1966
02:11:38,980 --> 02:11:41,070
不用了  吉米  我在趕時間
No, Jimmy. I'm in a hurry!

1967
02:11:41,410 --> 02:11:44,210
我媽在看孩子  我得回去
My mom's watching the kids! I got to get home!

1968
02:11:44,380 --> 02:11:45,870
以後再來拿
I'll come back later!

1969
02:12:08,340 --> 02:12:09,970
凱倫
Karen!

1970
02:12:14,480 --> 02:12:15,500
發生什麼事了
What happened?

1971
02:12:16,910 --> 02:12:17,940
沒事
Nothing.

1972
02:12:18,550 --> 02:12:20,450
- 到底什麼事  - 我只是突然怕起來了
- What happened? - I just got scared.

1973
02:12:23,950 --> 02:12:25,080
車鑰匙拿了沒有
Got the keys?

1974
02:12:26,860 --> 02:12:30,490
- 到底什麼事  - 我只是害怕起來了
- What happened, Karen? - I just got scared. It's okay.

1975
02:12:30,660 --> 02:12:32,250
- 沒事吧  - 現在沒事了
- Are you all right? - Yeah.

1976
02:12:39,170 --> 02:12:43,730
如果你是黑手黨員  你永遠不會知道幾時會被殺
If you're part of a crew, nobody ever tells you they're going to kill you.

1977
02:12:44,280 --> 02:12:46,040
沒人會事先通知你的
It doesn't happen that way.

1978
02:12:46,210 --> 02:12:49,650
也不像電影裏先大吵大罵
There aren't any arguments or curses like in the movies.

1979
02:12:49,810 --> 02:12:53,880
來殺你的人面帶笑容  像是你很親近的朋友
Your murderers come with smiles. They come as your friends.

1980
02:12:54,050 --> 02:12:56,080
他們一直很關心你
People who cared for you all your life.

1981
02:12:56,250 --> 02:13:00,620
在你有困難時  他們總會來幫助你
They always seem to come when you're weakest and most in need of their help.

1982
02:13:00,990 --> 02:13:04,220
所以我跟吉米約好在人多的地方見面
So I met Jimmy in a crowded place we both knew.

1983
02:13:04,600 --> 02:13:08,590
我早到了15分鐘  可吉米已經比我先到了
I got there 15 minutes early, and Jimmy was already there.

1984
02:13:09,030 --> 02:13:13,440
他佔了靠窗的雅座  凡是來餐廳的人  他都看得見
He took the booth near the window so he could see everyone who drove up.

1985
02:13:13,770 --> 02:13:16,140
他要確認我沒有被跟蹤
He wanted to make sure I wasn't tailed.

1986
02:13:16,570 --> 02:13:19,440
他很緊張  什麼也沒吃
He was jumpy. He hadn't touched a thing.

1987
02:13:20,480 --> 02:13:23,500
表面看來一點也沒事
On the surface, everything was supposed to be fine.

1988
02:13:23,680 --> 02:13:26,010
我們應該是要商量我的案子
We were supposed to be discussing my case.

1989
02:13:26,180 --> 02:13:31,120
但我可以感覺到吉米在試探我是否會為了救自己而出賣他
But I had a feeling Jimmy was trying to sense if I'd rat on him to save my neck.

1990
02:13:32,790 --> 02:13:36,520
我一直提醒你  不要在電話上談事情
I been telling you your whole life, don't talk on the phone.

1991
02:13:36,730 --> 02:13:38,520
現在你明白了
Now you understand?

1992
02:13:41,170 --> 02:13:44,500
我想你勝訴的機會很大  一切會沒問題的
It's going to be okay. You got a good chance to beat the case.

1993
02:13:47,670 --> 02:13:51,940
那個小子  你知道我是在說誰吧
You know that kid from the city we were talking about? You know?

1994
02:13:54,350 --> 02:13:58,580
那是個告密者  他一被捕就把所有的人都招供出來了
The kid turned out to be a rat. As soon as he got pinched, he ratted on everybody.

1995
02:14:01,350 --> 02:14:03,290
我知道他現在躲在哪裏
I know where he is. He's hiding now.

1996
02:14:05,220 --> 02:14:06,550
懂不懂我說的
Know what I'm saying?

1997
02:14:11,530 --> 02:14:14,690
你想你能和安東尼一方面度假  一方面把他解決掉嗎
Would you have a problem going with Anthony to take care of that?

1998
02:14:17,800 --> 02:14:18,860
沒問題
No, not at all.

1999
02:14:20,670 --> 02:14:22,260
這樣他們就沒證人了
That way they got nothing.

2000
02:14:31,120 --> 02:14:33,850
吉米從來沒有叫我替他除掉任何人
Jimmy had never asked me to whack somebody before.

2001
02:14:34,320 --> 02:14:37,980
現在他叫我和安東尼一起到佛羅里達去為他殺人
But now he's asking me to go to Florida and do a hit with Anthony.

2002
02:14:45,530 --> 02:14:48,860
那時候我就知道  如果我去了佛州  我不會活著回來
That's when I knew I would never have come back from Florida alive.

2003
02:15:03,650 --> 02:15:06,550
不論你要把我們搬去哪裏  我說過
Whenever you move me, I asked once and I'll tell you again...

2004
02:15:06,720 --> 02:15:08,550
我不去寒冷的地方
I don't want to go any place cold.

2005
02:15:09,550 --> 02:15:11,710
你並沒有選擇餘地
You don't have a choice in that matter.

2006
02:15:12,120 --> 02:15:14,650
到底是誰管這個
Come on. Whoever fucking controls it...

2007
02:15:15,460 --> 02:15:18,090
幫個忙  只要不是寒冷地方就行
just no place cold. Do that for me. I'm trying to...

2008
02:15:18,260 --> 02:15:19,990
他有氣管炎
He's bronchial, that's why.

2009
02:15:20,160 --> 02:15:22,720
如果檢查後他真有氣管炎  我們會列入考慮因素
If he's legitimately bronchial, we'll consider that.

2010
02:15:22,900 --> 02:15:25,100
我希望去不冷的地方
I'd like to go someplace not cold.

2011
02:15:25,270 --> 02:15:29,000
我能問一些問題嗎  我父母會怎麼樣
Can I ask you some questions? What about my parents?

2012
02:15:30,110 --> 02:15:31,100
他們怎麼啦
What about them?

2013
02:15:31,280 --> 02:15:33,770
我能不能見他們  跟他們通消息
Am I going to see them? Am I going to talk to them?

2014
02:15:35,010 --> 02:15:37,410
怎麼跟他們聯絡
Don't I have some kind of contact with them?

2015
02:15:38,080 --> 02:15:39,110
不能
No.

2016
02:15:40,250 --> 02:15:43,580
等一等  你是說
Wait a minute. Wait a minute. You mean to tell me that...

2017
02:15:43,950 --> 02:15:47,980
就算我父母生病了  我也不能去看他們嗎
God forbid something happens to my parents, they get sick, I can't see them?

2018
02:15:48,160 --> 02:15:51,150
也許可以特別安排  如果他們病了
Maybe something can be worked out if they're sick...

2019
02:15:51,630 --> 02:15:53,790
情形特殊的話
if there's extraordinary circumstances...

2020
02:15:53,960 --> 02:15:56,830
我不能這樣做  亨利
I can't do this. I can't do this, Henry.

2021
02:15:57,940 --> 02:15:59,700
我不能留下我父母不管
I can't leave my parents.

2022
02:16:00,940 --> 02:16:03,130
抱歉  凱倫  我跟你說了
Excuse me, Karen, I told you before.

2023
02:16:04,410 --> 02:16:07,400
除非你跟孩子們和我在一起  我不會同意這個證人保護行動
I'm not going to do this unless you and the kids come with me.

2024
02:16:09,750 --> 02:16:11,410
我沒有辦法一個人捱過這些
I can't do it without you.

2025
02:16:11,850 --> 02:16:15,910
你要怎麼做就怎麼做  可是  就這樣
So, you do whatever, but... that's it.

2026
02:16:17,450 --> 02:16:19,980
- 你們需要亨利  並不需要我  對不對  - 沒錯
- You need Henry, not me, right? - That's right.

2027
02:16:20,360 --> 02:16:22,790
老實說  我並不在乎你去不去
Frankly, I don't care whether you go or not.

2028
02:16:23,090 --> 02:16:26,360
如果能使他成為一個快樂而有用的證人  我希望你去
If it'll make him a better witness, I'd like you to be with him.

2029
02:16:26,530 --> 02:16:28,230
他們要的是亨利  不是我
They want Henry, not me.

2030
02:16:28,400 --> 02:16:31,460
亨利會受到保護  他們動不了他
Henry'll be in the protection program. They can't get to him.

2031
02:16:32,400 --> 02:16:35,840
他們只能從你跟孩子身上動手來傷害亨利
They can only get to him by getting to you or your kids.

2032
02:16:36,010 --> 02:16:38,410
假如他參與這次行動  你的處境就很危險
If he goes into the program, you're in danger...

2033
02:16:38,580 --> 02:16:41,010
- 我什麼也不知道呀  - 不要給我
- I don't know anything. - Don't give me...

2034
02:16:41,180 --> 02:16:42,540
天真無邪那一套
the babe-in-the-woods routine.

2035
02:16:42,710 --> 02:16:47,280
我聽過那些電話錄音  你在電話中大談白粉
I've listened to those wiretaps, and I've heard you talk about cocaine.

2036
02:16:47,450 --> 02:16:50,650
你跟亨利一通電話接著一通
Conversation after conversation you talked to Henry on the phone.

2037
02:16:55,930 --> 02:16:57,950
不管他是進監牢
It doesn't matter. Whether he goes to jail...

2038
02:16:58,130 --> 02:17:01,430
還是勝訴了  他都一樣是沒命
or stays on the streets and beats the case, he's a dead man.

2039
02:17:02,170 --> 02:17:03,900
你們心裏都很清楚
He knows it and you know it.

2040
02:17:05,540 --> 02:17:07,160
我們的孩子怎麼辦  他們要上學呀
What about the kids and school?

2041
02:17:07,340 --> 02:17:09,600
總不能把他們留下
Will they get left back? I mean, what goes on?

2042
02:17:10,010 --> 02:17:12,500
你們為什麼不到華爾街去抓那些真正的壞人
Go to Wall Street and get real crooks.

2043
02:17:12,880 --> 02:17:15,440
賣西裝給你們的人  真有幽默感
Whoever sold you those suits had a sense of humor.

2044
02:17:15,610 --> 02:17:18,450
歸根結底  和我們配合才是唯一救你們的方法
What it comes down to is we're your only salvation.

2045
02:17:19,150 --> 02:17:22,590
我們會保障你們的生命  也會不讓他去坐牢
We'll save your life and his life, and we'll keep you out of jail.

2046
02:17:26,820 --> 02:17:29,660
今天早上你曾把你的背景向陪審團說明
This morning you told the jury about your background.

2047
02:17:29,830 --> 02:17:31,660
要從人群中消失並不是一件困難的事
It was easy for us to disappear.

2048
02:17:32,000 --> 02:17:34,120
房子是岳母的名字
My house was in my mother-in-law's name.

2049
02:17:34,300 --> 02:17:36,270
車是我老婆的名字
My cars were registered to my wife.

2050
02:17:36,430 --> 02:17:39,870
社會福利卡以及駕照都是假的
My Social Security cards and driver's licenses were phonies.

2051
02:17:40,040 --> 02:17:42,400
沒投過票  沒繳過稅
I never voted or paid taxes.

2052
02:17:42,970 --> 02:17:47,430
唯一能表示有我這個人存在的是出生證明和犯罪記錄
My birth certificate and arrest sheet was all you'd ever have to know I was alive.

2053
02:17:47,610 --> 02:17:50,140
- 那個人在法庭內嗎  - 是的
- Do you see him here in this courtroom? - Yes.

2054
02:17:50,580 --> 02:17:52,880
你能為陪審團將他指證出來嗎
Will you please point him out for the jury?

2055
02:17:55,590 --> 02:18:00,180
法官大人  請記錄下來  希爾先生已正式指證了詹姆斯·康威
Let the record reflect that Mr. Hill identified the defendant, James Conway.

2056
02:18:01,330 --> 02:18:04,420
你也認識一位叫保羅·西席羅的人
Do you also know a man named Paul Cicero?

2057
02:18:04,760 --> 02:18:06,750
- 那個人在這個法庭內嗎  - 是的
- Do you see him in the courtroom? - Yes.

2058
02:18:07,330 --> 02:18:09,230
你能為陪審團將他指證出來嗎
Can you point him out for the jury?

2059
02:18:11,200 --> 02:18:15,330
法官大人  請記錄下希爾先生已指證了保羅·西席羅
Let the record reflect that Mr. Hill identified the defendant, Paul Cicero.

2060
02:18:16,640 --> 02:18:18,340
法官大人  我這裏有一份文件
Your Honor, I have a document...

2061
02:18:18,510 --> 02:18:20,910
對我來說  最困難的就是從那種生活方式中走出來
The hardest thing was leaving the life.

2062
02:18:21,680 --> 02:18:23,200
我還是喜愛那種生活
I still love the life.

2063
02:18:23,610 --> 02:18:25,710
我們像電影明星一樣被禮遇
We were treated like movie stars with muscle.

2064
02:18:25,880 --> 02:18:27,940
只要開口  要什麼有什麼
We had it all, just for the asking.

2065
02:18:28,120 --> 02:18:31,450
老婆  母親  孩子  人人都能享受
Our wives, mothers, kids, everybody rode along.

2066
02:18:31,760 --> 02:18:34,920
一包紙袋的珠寶藏在廚房
I had paper bags filled with jewelry stashed in the kitchen.

2067
02:18:35,090 --> 02:18:37,360
一缸白粉就放在床邊
I had a sugar bowl full of coke next to the bed.

2068
02:18:37,530 --> 02:18:41,330
稱為鼠輩  是因為老鼠為了求生存  什麼事都會做
People call them rats because rats do anything to survive. Isn't that right?

2069
02:18:41,500 --> 02:18:43,520
- 抗議  - 抗議成立
- Objection! - Objection sustained.

2070
02:18:43,700 --> 02:18:46,900
- 至於老鼠我就不知道了  - 你太瞭解了
- I know nothing about being a rat. - You know everything about it.

2071
02:18:49,110 --> 02:18:51,600
只要一通電話  什麼都有
Anything I wanted was a phone call away.

2072
02:18:51,780 --> 02:18:55,210
免費的汽車  城裏所有的黑幫分子玩樂的地方都能自由進出
Free cars. Keys to a dozen hideout flats all over the city.

2073
02:18:55,380 --> 02:18:57,870
一個週末可以下注兩三萬
I'd bet $20,000, $30,000 over a weekend...

2074
02:18:58,050 --> 02:19:02,210
也可以一周內把贏的錢全花光  有時候也借高利貸來還賭債
then blow the winnings in a week or go to the sharks to pay the bookies.

2075
02:19:02,390 --> 02:19:03,440
不過一點關係都沒有
It didn't matter.

2076
02:19:04,150 --> 02:19:09,020
錢花光了  我只要出去多搶一點就行了
It didn't mean anything. When I was broke I would go out and rob some more.

2077
02:19:09,430 --> 02:19:10,830
我們控制一切
We ran everything.

2078
02:19:11,360 --> 02:19:15,630
收買條子  收買律師  甚至收買法官
We paid off cops. We paid off lawyers. We paid off judges.

2079
02:19:15,900 --> 02:19:19,340
每個人都受賄  只要我們肯出錢
Everybody had their hands out. Everything was for the taking.

2080
02:19:21,440 --> 02:19:22,930
現在都結束了
And now it's all over.

2081
02:19:23,870 --> 02:19:25,310
難就難在這裏
That's the hardest part.

2082
02:19:26,340 --> 02:19:27,940
如今一切都不同了
Today everything is different.

2083
02:19:28,110 --> 02:19:32,280
我得像其他人一樣等排班
There's no action. I have to wait around like everyone else.

2084
02:19:32,680 --> 02:19:34,450
連像樣的菜都吃不到
Can't even get decent food.

2085
02:19:35,220 --> 02:19:38,350
我搬來以後曾點過意大利面  加意大利蕃茄配料
After I got here I ordered spaghetti with marinara sauce...

2086
02:19:38,520 --> 02:19:40,320
結果上的是雞蛋面加蕃茄醬
and I got egg noodles and ketchup.

2087
02:19:41,190 --> 02:19:42,680
我成為了無名小卒淡泊一生
I'm an average nobody.

2088
02:19:44,060 --> 02:19:46,830
下半輩子得過得像個可憐蟲
I get to live the rest of my life like a schnook.

2089
02:19:57,840 --> 02:20:06,100
亨利·希爾目前仍在接受證人保護行動
他於1987年在西雅圖以販毒罪名被捕
但得到緩刑五年  此後不曾再犯罪

2090
02:20:07,380 --> 02:20:13,060
1989年  亨利與凱倫在婚後25年正式離婚

2091
02:20:15,120 --> 02:20:21,920
保羅·西席羅因呼吸道問題1988年死於監獄  享年73歲

2092
02:20:23,910 --> 02:20:32,300
吉米·康威目前仍在紐約州監獄以謀殺的罪名服刑
他必須等到2004年  他78歲時才能獲得假釋

